title: Ya kol al sofoof
text: Ya kol al sofoof al sama-eyeen, ratelo le-eelahena be naghamat el-tasbeeh, wabe-tahegoo mana al-yowma fareheen, be-keyamat El-Sayed El-Maseeh.
